$interpreted: NEKO#ΦωΦ: Not a human in-sight. Just how deserted is this damn place? What do I do now...go back and wait first?
Roger: Kittyeyes!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: W-w-w-who are you!?
Roger: Eh, ah...y-you're not...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Ehhh~ Are you NEKO's fan?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Never thought NEKO's popularity would reach a completely different world~
Roger: Fan? What's a fan? Is it food?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: You don't know what a fan is? Then why did you approach NEKO?
Roger: Sorry, I made a mistake. I thought you were my little sister...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: ...If that little sister of yours looks just like you, NEKO's gonna be pretty flippin mad!
Roger: No...Sorry, I'm urgently trying to find her and I didn't bother to take a closer look. That's why I mistook you for her.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Looking for her? Your little sister is missing?
Roger: ...Yeah. Kittyeyes left without even leaving a note, so I have no idea where she went...
Dumb Bandit: Look, cat ears! That must be the Kittyeyes that boss mentioned, the one with a brother complex!
Simpleton Bandit: So does that mean the other person is Roger!? Sick! Two birds one stone, we get ALL the credit! Hahahaha──
NEKO#ΦωΦ: This kind of bearded old man is NOT what NEKO's into!! There are things you can and can't say to NEKO, and this is firmly in the "can't" section!!!
Dumb Bandit: HA! As if I'd believe that! Eat this!
Roger: Look out!!!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Woah, are these gold coins? They're probably worth a fortune if I can bring them back...
Roger: You can have all these. Take it as compensation for getting you involved in this mess.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: What? But NEKO...
Roger: Looks like a group of bandits is looking for Kittyeyes and me. I have to find her as soon as possible and protect her!
Roger: I got to go now. Later!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: But NEKO still doesn't know how to go back...
